==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfetter
<hw>Un*fet"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>fetter</ets>.]</ety> <def>To loose from fetters or
from restraint; to unchain; to unshackle; to liberate; <as>as, to
<ex>unfetter</ex> the mind</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfeudalize</ent>⟦br⟧
